The women in question were stunned about how the escalator worked at the shopping mall and they took turns in mounting it. Some of them expressed fears about mounting the structure which is designed to move people to a height and also lower them. It appears such ultra modern facilities are rare sights in the state. They were seen clapping and dancing as they played around the structure. Social media users have reacted to the viral video hilariously. Watch the video below: Nigerian Women Today Spotted Dancing, Singing and Jubilating After Entering An Escalator For The First Time Ever In Their Lives At A Mall In Ebonyi State!!! A post shared by  Gossip Mill Nigeria (@gossipmillnaija) on Jul 28, 2019 at 3:55pm PDT Source